Name: Numba Deluxe

Get ready for some great fun and absorbing gameplay through 3 testing game modes as you strive to become the ultimate Numba Champion in this all-new puzzler. Features: Stunning Graphics and Effects Combos, Bonuses, Gems and more High Score Tables for all your scores
